!
! DSLL implementation of a full adder
!

! rails

set vdd p
set vss g

macro inv input output

p vdd input output
n vss input output

endmac

wp vdd sn sp ! output driver
wp vdd sp sn
n sp bp n1 ! left side
n sn bn n1
n n1 ap n3
n n2 an n3
n n3 cn vss
n sp bn n2 ! right side
n sn bp n2
n n1 an n4
n n2 ap n4
n n4 cp vss

inv ap an ! form inversions
inv bp bn
inv cp cn

set ap 0 0 1 10 0 20 1 30 0 40 1 50 0 60 1 70
set bp 0 0      1 20      0 40      1 60
set cp 0 0                1 40

format ap bp cp sp sn

page
step 74
